description: "Bundle of the MCP & contract platform epic (pm-5k4v) plus SDK package-authoring docs (pm-ugqx) into one coherent PR. Children: pm-hywv+pm-77t3 (narrow MCP tools pm_notes/pm_learnings/pm_deps; 18->21 tools), pm-qxwu (TOOL_SCHEMA_BASE additionalProperties typo-swallow hardening via unknown-key warning), pm-fd8n (generate pm_run action-list from PM_TOOL_ACTIONS to end prose/enum drift), pm-r9sz (export PM_TOOL_PARAMETERS_SCHEMA_VERSION constant + bind assertion sites), pm-kl11 (MCP initialize+tools/list+unknown-tool handshake tests), pm-te9x (capture_level docs for extension authors), pm-k5r6 (create vs mutateItem dual write-path contract docs). Delivered via specialized sub-agents on disjoint file sets, integrated/built/tested/changelog-regenerated by orchestrator. NO commit/push this run."
