  "2026-06-05T15:51:34.572Z",codex-sdk-cli-continuation,"CI review-loop fix for PR #113: Docs/Skills failed because docs/EXTENSIONS.md exceeded the 450-line public-doc limit (555 lines) and code-fence comments were counted as extra top-level headings. Split detailed telemetry.capture_level and create-vs-mutateItem write-path guidance into docs/EXTENSION_AUTHOR_CONTRACTS.md, kept docs/EXTENSIONS.md at 435 lines with one top-level heading, and linked the new doc from pm docs. Local rechecks passed: pnpm quality:docs-skills; pnpm quality:static; pnpm build; pnpm changelog:pm:check; pnpm contracts:check; git diff --check. Timestamp-only pm-changelog managed-extension churn restored before staging."
  "2026-06-05T16:02:42.842Z",codex-sdk-cli-continuation,"CI review-loop fix for PR #113 static gate: remote contracts:check failed because scripts/contracts-snapshot.mjs inherited local PM_GLOBAL_PATH/global extensions when generating the golden fixture. That polluted tests/fixtures/contracts/full.json with a user-global beads import command that CI correctly did not have. Hardened scripts/contracts-snapshot.mjs to run pm contracts with an isolated temporary PM_GLOBAL_PATH, regenerated tests/fixtures/contracts/full.json from the deterministic clean surface, and verified locally: pnpm contracts:check; pnpm quality:static; pnpm quality:docs-skills; pnpm changelog:pm:check; git diff --check. Timestamp-only pm-changelog managed-extension churn restored before staging."
  "2026-06-05T16:05:40.900Z",codex-sdk-cli-continuation,"Reviewer follow-up for PR #113: addressed Gemini robustness findings. Changes: processRpcLine now rejects non-object/non-array JSON-RPC payloads with -32600 instead of crashing on null; detectUnexpectedTopLevelKeys defensively returns no warnings for non-object args; createSerialQueue.idle now waits on an explicit pending count/drain waiter so it cannot resolve while tasks enqueued during active drain remain pending; scripts/contracts-snapshot.mjs now reports spawnSync startup errors explicitly, guards stderr/stdout writes, and still cleans isolated PM_GLOBAL_PATH in finally. Regression coverage added for processRpcLine('null') invalid-request response and idle waiting through a task enqueued while active. Local verification passed: pnpm build; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/shared-helpers.spec.ts tests/integration/mcp-handshake.spec.ts tests/unit/contracts-command.spec.ts (43 tests); pnpm typecheck; pnpm contracts:check; pnpm quality:static; git diff --check."
  "2026-06-05T16:10:35.870Z",codex-sdk-cli-continuation,"Reviewer follow-up for PR #113 current-head Gemini finding: JSON-RPC notifications (requests without an id member) now suppress both success and error responses in processRpcLine, while malformed non-object payloads still return invalid-request with id null. Added regression coverage for tools/list and unsupported-method notifications writing no stdout. Local verification passed: pnpm build; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/integration/mcp-handshake.spec.ts tests/unit/shared-helpers.spec.ts (25 tests); pnpm typecheck; pnpm quality:static."
  "2026-06-05T16:19:48.170Z",codex-sdk-cli-continuation,"CI coverage fix for PR #113: latest coverage run failed because serial-queue.ts branch coverage missed the immediate idle() path after the explicit pending-count/drain-waiter hardening. Added a regression test for idle() resolving immediately when the queue is empty. Local verification passed: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/shared-helpers.spec.ts tests/integration/mcp-handshake.spec.ts (26 tests); pnpm typecheck; git diff --check; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage (139 files, 2318 tests, 100% statements/branches/functions/lines)."
  "2026-06-05T16:30:02.500Z",codex-sdk-cli-continuation,"Review follow-up evidence: implemented JSON-RPC parse errors as code -32700 in MCP stdio, added malformed-line coverage, and made contract snapshot serialization recursively sort object keys for deterministic output. Verification passed: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/integration/mcp-handshake.spec.ts tests/unit/shared-helpers.spec.ts (27 tests), pnpm contracts:check, pnpm typecheck, pnpm quality:static, pnpm quality:docs-skills, node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage (139 files, 2319 tests, 100% statements/branches/functions/lines)."
